OL,3,CTroubles civil claims a green-field
OL,4,Csite for lawyers, Boutcher tells MPs
OL,6,FThe "attritional" approach of security
OL,7,Fagencies in dealing with Troubles
OL,8,Fcompensation claims is creating a
OL,9,F"green-field site for lawyers", Jon
OL,10,FBoutcher has said.
OL,12,FThe PSNI Chief Constable told MPs on
OL,13,Fthe Northern Ireland Affairs Committee
OL,14,Fthat the force had paid out more than
OL,15,Ftwice as much to lawyers as it did to
OL,16,Fvictims in civil claims over a six-
OL,17,Fyear period.
