OL,3,CTroubles civil claims a green-field
OL,4,Csite for lawyers, Boutcher tells MPs
OL,6,FUnder the Legacy Act introduced by the
OL,7,Fprevious UK government, the
OL,8,FIndependent Commission for
OL,9,FReconciliation and Information
OL,10,FRecovery (ICRIR), has taken on the
OL,11,Fresponsibility from the PSNI to carry
OL,12,Fout investigations into deaths and
OL,13,Fserious harm related to the Troubles
OL,14,Fwhich occurred between January 1 1966
OL,15,Fand April 10 1998.
OL,17,FHowever, MPs were told that the Act
OL,18,Fhad not diminished legacy costs for
OL,19,Fthe force, and may actually increase
OL,20,Fthem.
