OL,6,FMr Boutcher said when policing powers
OL,7,Fwere devolved to Stormont, there was
OL,8,Fno agreement over how legacy
OL,9,Finvestigations would be funded within
OL,10,Fthe police.
OL,12,FHe said: "We have a legacy
OL,13,Finvestigation branch that was the
OL,14,Fsuccessor unit to the HET (Historical
OL,15,FEnquiries Team).
OL,17,F"That unit cost #5.3 million a year to
OL,18,Ffund.
