OL,6,F"We also have ongoing civil cases.
OL,7,FThat's over #3 million a year it costs
OL,8,Fto deal with those cases."
OL,10,FThe Chief Constable added: "Between
OL,11,F2018 and 2024, the PSNI resolved 30
OL,12,Fchallenging civil cases. In those
OL,13,Fcases we paid out to families,
OL,14,Fclaimants, victims, a total of #25
OL,15,Fmillion, which we are not funded for.
OL,17,F"Of that #25 million, I am told that
OL,18,F#7.3 million went to the victims, the
OL,19,Fclaimants themselves; #17.7 million
OL,20,Fwent to the lawyers.
